{"title":"RequestR以及response基础","date":"2019-03-29T09:04:21.000Z","link":"Java Web/Request Response","comments":true,"tags":["Java Web"],"categories":["Java Web"],"updated":"2019-10-24T07:52:55.198Z","content":"  <a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"Request以及Response的基础概念以及使用\">Request以及Response的基础概念以及使用<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#Request以及Response的基础概念以及使用\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"Request\">Request<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#Request\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"Requst的原理\">Requst的原理<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#Requst的原理\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>tomcat服务器 根据url中的资源路径，创建servlet的对象</li>\n<li>tomcat 创建resquest 和response 对象 request对象 封装请求消息数据</li>\n<li>tomcat 将resquest 和 response 给 service 方法 给service方法，并调用</li>\n<li>程序员 接受 到信息对齐处理， 通过response 相应</li>\n<li>服务器在浏览器相应之前 从response对象设置相应的消息数据</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"Request的继承的体系结构\">Request的继承的体系结构<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#Request的继承的体系结构\"></a></h4><p>ServletRequeset</p>\n<p>​        | 继承</p>\n<p>HttpServletRequest</p>\n<p>​        |实现</p>\n<p>org.apache.catalina.connector.RequestFacade</p>\n<h4 id=\"Request的功能\">Request的功能<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#Request的功能\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li><p>获取请求消息</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>请求行</p>\n<p>GET /a/demo?name = 1 HTTP/1.1</p>\n<p>方法</p>\n<ol>\n<li><font size color=\"red\">请求方法 GET</font>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getMethod</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><font size color=\"red\">虚拟目录 /a</font>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getContextPath</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>Servlet路径/demo</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getServletPath</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>获取uri</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// http://localhost/servlet/demo</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getRequestURI</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"> <span class=\"comment\">//   /servlet/demo</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getRequestURL</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>获取协议</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getProrocol</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>ip地址</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getRemoteAddr</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li><p>请求头</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>方法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//请求头的名称</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getHeader</span><span class=\"params\">(String name)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">Enumeration&lt;E&gt; <span class=\"title\">getHeadernames</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        Enumeration&lt;String&gt; headerNames = request.getHeaderNames();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(headerNames.hasMoreElements())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String name = headerNames.nextElement();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            String value = request.getHeader(name);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(name +<span class=\"string\">\" :\"</span>+ value);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"comment\">// 获取请求头的数据 例如 jsp 页面中过去的资源， referer 就是这个</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//判断假连接</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    String referer = request.getHeader(<span class=\"string\">\"referer\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (referer != <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// day 表示项目中正确的目录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (referer.contains(<span class=\"string\">\"/day)\"</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\" is correct website\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"this is the fake website\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> System.out.println(referer);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>2. user-agent \n\n   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">   String agent = request.getHeader(<span class=\"string\">\"user-agent\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> ( agent.contains(<span class=\"string\">\"Chrome\"</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\" this is Chrome\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\" this is others \"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</code></pre><ul>\n<li><p>请求体</p>\n<p>只用post请求才有请求方式   ，才有请求体 分装了post对象</p>\n<p>步骤</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>获取流对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//过去字符输入流</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"function\">BufferedReader <span class=\"title\">getReader</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//获取字节输入流 操作说有类型的数据</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"function\">ServletInputStream <span class=\"title\">getinputStream</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">          BufferedReader reader = request.getReader();</span><br><span class=\"line\">          String  line = reader.readLine();</span><br><span class=\"line\">          <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(line != <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">              System.out.println(line);</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>2. 在流对象中拿数据\n</code></pre><ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>其他的功能</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>获取请求参数（<font color=\"red\">使用 get  post 都可以以使用</font>）</p>\n<ol>\n<li>String getParameter（String name） // username = zhangsan</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre><code>2. String [] getParamterValues(String name) 获取参数值的数组\n</code></pre>   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">     String[] pvs = request.getParameterValues(<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(String c : pvs)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         System.out.println(c);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<pre><code>3. Enmeration &lt;String&gt; getParameterNames() 获取请求参数 的名称\n\n   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> Enumeration&lt;String&gt; pvn = request.getParameterNames();</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (pvn.hasMoreElements())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         String name = pvn.nextElement();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 返回一个</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">         String value = request.getParameter(name);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    System.out.println(name + value);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">     &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n4. Map&lt;String, String[]&gt;  getParameterMap() 获取参数的map集合\n\n   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> Map&lt;String, String[]&gt; parameterMap = request.getParameterMap();</span><br><span class=\"line\"> Set&lt;String&gt; keyset = parameterMap.keySet();</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (String name : keyset)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">String [] values = parameterMap.get(name);</span><br><span class=\"line\">     System.out.println(name);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (String value : values)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         System.out.println(value);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"-----\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</code></pre><ul>\n<li>乱码问题</li>\n</ul>\n<p>   get tomcat在v8以上的版本已经解决了</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>post问题：</p>\n<pre><code><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">request.setCharacterEncoding(<span class=\"string\">\"utf-8\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><p>请求转发：一种在服务器内部的资源跳转</p>\n<p>步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>通过request 对象获取请求转发的器 RequestDispatcher（String path）</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>通过RequestDispatcher对象来进行转发 ：使用forward(ServletRequest request, ServletResponse response)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">RequestDispatcher requestDispatcher = request.getRequestDispatcher(<span class=\"string\">\"/dome2\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">     requestDispatcher.forward(request, response);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>   改进</p>\n   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">request.getRequestDispatcher(<span class=\"string\">\"/a\"</span>).forward(request, response);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>   特点：\n\n1. 浏览器的地址栏 路径没有变化\n   2. 只能访问当前项目内部的资源中\n3. 转发是一次请求\n</code></pre><ul>\n<li><p>共享数据</p>\n<p>域对象：一个有范围的对象，可以在范围内数据共享</p>\n<p>   request 域：代表一次请求的范围， 一般用于请求转发多个资源的共享数据</p>\n<p>方法：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"number\">1</span>. <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"params\">(String name, Object obj)</span> 存储 类似于key value</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">2. Object <span class=\"title\">getAttribute</span><span class=\"params\">(String name)</span>  获取属性对象</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">   3. <span class=\"title\">removeAttribute</span><span class=\"params\">(String name)</span> 删除属性对象</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><p>获取ServletContext</p>\n   <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ServletContext getServletContext()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Http协议\">Http协议<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#Http协议\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li><p>请求消息 客户端发给服务器</p>\n<p>数据格式：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>请求行</li>\n<li>请求头</li>\n<li>请求空行</li>\n<li>请求体</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>相应消息</p>\n<p>数据格式：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>响应行</p>\n<p>协议以及版本  HTTP 1.1 200 OK</p>\n<p>状态码：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>1XX：server接受到host的消息 但是 没有接受完成等待一段时间后 发送1XX的状态吗</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>2XX：表示成功 200</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>3xx ：表示重定想 302 （重定向） 304（访问缓存）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>4xx ：客户端错误 </p>\n<p>404 路径存在问题</p>\n<p>405 请求方式没有对的doXXx方法</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>5xx ：服务器的端错误，服务器内存存在问题</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>响应头</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>格式 ： 头名称： 值</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>常见的响应头</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>Context-Tpye ：响应的客户端本次响应的数据以及编码的 格式</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Content-Length </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Content-dispositon server告诉客户端以什么格式打开响应体数据</p>\n<p>值默认 in-line</p>\n<p>attachment ：以附件的形式打开 文件</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>响应空行</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>响应体</p>\n<p>HTTP 1.1 200 ok</p>\n<p>Context-type:</p>\n<p>Context-Length :</p>\n<p>Date</p>\n<p>加上html内容</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"Response对象\">Response对象<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#Response对象\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"功能\">功能<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#功能\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li><p>设置响应 消息</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>格式 HTTP/1.1 200 OK</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置状态码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">setStatus(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> sc)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置响应头</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">setHeader(String name, String value)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置响应体</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>获取输出流</p>\n<p>​    字符输出流</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">PrinterWriter <span class=\"title\">getWriter</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>​    字节输出流</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">ServletOutPutStream <span class=\"title\">getOutputStream</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"使用\">使用<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#使用\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li><p>重定向</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">response.setStatus(<span class=\"number\">302</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">response.setHeader(<span class=\"string\">\"location\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"/day/demo2\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>改进</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">response.sendRedirect(<span class=\"string\">\"/day/demo2\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>转发的特点</p>\n<ol>\n<li>浏览器的地址栏 路径没有变化</li>\n<li>只能访问当前项目服务器内部的资源中</li>\n<li>转发是一次请求 <font color=\"red\">能使用request对象共享数据</font></li>\n</ol>\n<p>重定向</p>\n<ol>\n<li>地址发生变化</li>\n<li>可以访问其他站点的资源</li>\n<li>两次的请求 <font color=\"red\">不能使用request对象共享数据</font></li>\n</ol>\n<font color=\"red\">路径写法</font>\n\n<p>​    绝对路径：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>相对路径</p>\n<p>./index.html（./可以省略）</p>\n<p>( ../)代表着当前目录的后退页面</p>\n<p>不以/开头</p>\n<p>规则：确定访问的当前的资源  和目标资源之间的相对位置关系 </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>绝对路径：通过唯一的路径确定唯一的资源</p>\n<p>以/开头的路径</p>\n<p>从客户端 到server需要使用  虚拟目录（就是项目的目录）</p>\n<p>server之间转发不需要写虚拟目录 </p>\n<p>重定向需要加虚拟目录</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>建议使用动态获取虚拟目录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">String contextPath = request.getContextPath();</span><br><span class=\"line\">response.sendRedirect(contextPath+<span class=\"string\">\"/demo\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>服务器到浏览器的字符输出字符输出（获取流对象之前设置编码）</li>\n</ol>\n   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//设置流的编码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">response.setCharacterEncoding(<span class=\"string\">\"GBK\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//告诉浏览器  server使用的数据的编码 保持一致， 但是他可以默认设置流的编码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">response.setHeader(<span class=\"string\">\"content-type\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"text/html;charset=GBK\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//简单的 形式设置编码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">response.setContentType(<span class=\"string\">\"text/html;charset=utf-8\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>字节输出流</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ServletOutputStream outputStream = response.getOutputStream();</span><br><span class=\"line\">       outputStream.write(<span class=\"string\">\"hello\"</span>.getBytes());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>验证码的使用</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>本质就是一张图片</p>\n<p>目的：放置恶意的表单的注册</p>\n<p>动态生成的过程</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>过程</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>创建对象，在内存中图片</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>美化图片</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>图片输出的到页面</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//1. new object</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">BufferedImage image = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> BufferedImage(<span class=\"number\">50</span>, <span class=\"number\">100</span>, BufferedImage.TYPE_3BYTE_BGR);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//美化页面</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//3.将图片生成到显示</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ImageIO.write(image, <span class=\"string\">\"jpg\"</span>, response.getOutputStream());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"ServletContext对象\">ServletContext对象<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#ServletContext对象\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li><p>概念：代表整个web应用，可以 和服务器通信</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>获取对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">requeset.getServletContext();</span><br><span class=\"line\">this.getServletContext();</span><br><span class=\"line\">//代表整个web应用对象地址是一致的</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>功能</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>mime类型</p>\n<p>在互联网通信文件的过程中定义的一种 文件的数据类型</p>\n<p>格式 text /html  image/jpeg</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ServletContext servletContext = req.getServletContext();</span><br><span class=\"line\">   String filename = <span class=\"string\">\"a.jpg\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">String mimeType = servletContext.getMimeType(filename);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   System.out.println(mimeType);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li><p>域对象</p>\n<p>获取所有用户的数据</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">setAttribute(String name, object value)</span><br><span class=\"line\">getAttribute(String name)</span><br><span class=\"line\">removeAttribute(String name) </span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br><span class=\"line\">   servletContext.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"ha\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"hello\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><p>获取文件的真实路径</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//找对对应的路径 在web目录下</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">String realPath = servletContext.getRealPath(<span class=\"string\">\"/a.txt\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">System.out.println(realPath);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//在src目录下添加</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">servletContext.getRealPath(<span class=\"string\">\"/WEB-INF/classes/a.txt\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">System.out.println(realPath);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"文件下载使用\">文件下载使用<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#文件下载使用\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"下载的使用\">下载的使用<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#下载的使用\"></a></h4><p>   关键代码    </p>\n   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">content-disposition:attachment;filename=</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>   使用下载文件的方式</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">http://localhost:8080/download.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>   注意路径的使用</p>\n   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@WebServlet</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"/user/*\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>   在html文件的写法 对应到servlet 页面中 简单一句话</p>\n   <figure class=\"highlight html\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"/user/serv?filename=3.jpg\"</span>&gt;</span> 图片<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>   下载的代码（字节流地传输）</p>\n   <figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 1.获取文件的名称</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">String filename = req.getParameter(<span class=\"string\">\"filename\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 2.使用字节流加载进内存</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 2.1 找到文件服务器的路径</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ServletContext context = req.getServletContext();</span><br><span class=\"line\">String path = context.getRealPath(<span class=\"string\">\"/image/\"</span> + filename);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//2.2字节流关联 写道response中</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">FileInputStream fis = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> FileInputStream(path);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 3 设置response的响应头  content-type 下载打开方式 content-disposition</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">String mimeType = context.getMimeType(filename);</span><br><span class=\"line\">resp.setHeader(<span class=\"string\">\"content-type\"</span>,mimeType);</span><br><span class=\"line\">resp.setHeader(<span class=\"string\">\"content-disposition\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"attachment;filename=\"</span>+filename);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 4.输入流写道输出流</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ServletOutputStream outputStream = resp.getOutputStream();</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">byte</span> [] buff = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"keyword\">byte</span>[<span class=\"number\">1024</span> * <span class=\"number\">8</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> len = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> ((len = fis.read(buff)) != -<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    outputStream.write(buff, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, len);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">fis.close();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"出先中文文件错误的问题\">出先中文文件错误的问题<a href=\"Java Web/Request Response#出先中文文件错误的问题\"></a></h4><p>在运行之前将文件名 更改</p>\n","prev":{"title":"JSTL使用","link":"Java Web/JSTL"},"next":{"title":"Listener使用","link":"Java Web/Listener"},"plink":"http://www.zqynn.cn/Java Web/Request Response/","toc":[{"title":"Request以及Response的基础概念以及使用","id":"Request以及Response的基础概念以及使用","index":"1","children":[{"title":"Request","id":"Request","index":"1.1","children":[{"title":"Requst的原理","id":"Requst的原理","index":"1.1.1"},{"title":"Request的继承的体系结构","id":"Request的继承的体系结构","index":"1.1.2"},{"title":"Request的功能","id":"Request的功能","index":"1.1.3"}]},{"title":"Http协议","id":"Http协议","index":"1.2"},{"title":"Response对象","id":"Response对象","index":"1.3","children":[{"title":"功能","id":"功能","index":"1.3.1"},{"title":"使用","id":"使用","index":"1.3.2"}]},{"title":"ServletContext对象","id":"ServletContext对象","index":"1.4"},{"title":"文件下载使用","id":"文件下载使用","index":"1.5","children":[{"title":"下载的使用","id":"下载的使用","index":"1.5.1"},{"title":"出先中文文件错误的问题","id":"出先中文文件错误的问题","index":"1.5.2"}]}]}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://www.zqynn.cn/Java Web/Request Response/\" title=\"RequestR以及response基础\">http://www.zqynn.cn/Java Web/Request Response/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}